</p>
 <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Cut all the ingredientse in cubes.</p>
        <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Mix them with mayo and salt.</p>
        <h4 id="kompot">Kompot</h4>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 20 min</li>
            <li>Serves: 6 cups</li>
        </ul>
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a3/Peach_kompot.JPG/800px-Peach_kompot.JPG" alt="Borscht" width = "400">
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th class="headings">Ingredients</th>
                    <th class="headings">Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Dry apricot</td>
                    <td>100 gramm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Apples</td>
                    <td>100 gramm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Pears</td>
                    <td>100 gramm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Raisins</td>
                    <td>100 gramm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Sugar</td>
                    <td>2 table spoon</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Put 1 gallon of water on the stove and boiled it.
</p>
 <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Wash up all ingredients, cut apples and pears, add everything to the water</p>
        <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Boiled for 10 min. Wait till it cools to serve.</p>
